Output settings.gif

Set FontSize 22
Set Width 2560
Set Height 1440
Set TypingSpeed 300ms

Hide
Type "k-hunter" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Ctrl+S
Sleep 10ms

Show
# Theme
Enter
Down 2
Enter@1s 2
Down 2
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Content words count
PageDown 2
Down 3
Type "+++++++"
Sleep 1s

# Typer dimensions
PageUp
Down 2
Type "++++"
Sleep 1s
Type@500ms "--"
Down 1
Type@1s "++-"

Sleep 2s
